{"tid":2364960,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺識噴香水既女仔會加好多分","createTime":"2021-01-13T11:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T13:34:04.000Z","uid":313692,"like":16,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2f03941531ca7628d63732bc328cace596851562","tid":2364960,"uid":313692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"基本上第一印象是最重要的，不外乎視覺同嗅覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實好多女仔都識著衫，但唔是個個人都會噴香水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實身上有香味是很易吸引到男孩子的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但噴香水都唔是鳩噴就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個男仔都有唔同嘅喜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己就唔鍾意太濃，最好就係淡香水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家同唔同意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90167c70462048be7b3fcaf509de489c28c82d43","tid":2364960,"uid":78295,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"93a727c7ff4edf326ca1184932927772765e6540","tid":2364960,"uid":46584,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"淡香水ok，如果個女仔體味好香已經唔使噴香水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e37b138e4bbe62d8808eee67e3a904ae55b76b2","tid":2364960,"uid":313692,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"93a727c7ff4edf326ca1184932927772765e6540","tid":2364960,"uid":46584,"like